title: Natalie Brooks Secrets of Treasure House - Hidden Object Puzzle
description:
Natalie Brooks: Secrets of Treasure House
Is there a better setting for an adventure 
game than an old house full of secret rooms 
and hidden corridors? No. And Treasure House 
has plenty of these and more!
Join Natalie Brooks, our intrepid heroine 
as she solves puzzles, finds hidden items and 
interacts with colorful characters, including 
a chief of police whose ambitions might not be 
on the right side of the law!
Get caught up in this amazing and mysterious 
story as you discover the Secrets of Treasure House!
Key Game Features

    * Dozens of puzzles
    * Hundreds of hidden items
    * The complete story
    * Unlimited game time
